<div class="mw-parser-output"><h1>Experience (XP)</h1>
<p>Experience is usually gained by killing monsters. The experience you gain is relative to your level compared to the monsters level.
</p><p>You gain no experience when killing players.
</p><p>If you are good and kill evil you get a bonus. Vice versa but not quite as large.
